lead_paragraph: FEEN--Eugene, passed away peacefully at his home on January 17 at the age of 97. Beloved husband of the late Rosalie Feen; survived by his children Susan Davey, David R. Feen, granddaughter Allyson Davey and sister Shirley Strasser. Before retiring he was President of Park Ave. Imports, a subsidiary of Seagram's. 1/3
